{"tid":2400220,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有冇人覺得林欣彤好underrated？內含不專業分析！","createTime":"2021-02-08T18:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T03:25:32.000Z","uid":367215,"like":10,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e51c22442046f41eabf0a0b45a1e6ffa34245c","tid":2400220,"uid":367215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:20:52.000Z","msg":"據我所知 香港belting音域闊嘅女歌手包括下面呢啲 全部都係現場range<br />\n杜麗莎C3-C6 (36度/3個八度)<br />\n陳慧嫻A#2-G5 (33度/2.75個八度)<br />\n林憶蓮D3-G#5 (30度/2.5個八度)<br />\n彭羚D3-G5 (29度/2.4個八度)<br />\n葉倩文 D3-G#5 (30度/2.5個八度)<br />\n容祖兒C#3-G5 (30度/2.5個八度)<br />\n鄧紫棋C3-A5 (33度/2.75個八度)<br />\n林欣彤C#3-F#5 (29度/2.4個八度)<br />\n仲有例如GIN LEE 同關心妍都係 ?-G5<br />\n跟住發現其實裡面大部分都係老歌手 90後淨係得gem同林欣彤<br />\n當gem混成宇宙漿嘅時候 林欣彤直頭係接近失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iY4vVT9HI9M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiY4vVT9HI9M&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=9916fd89\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iY4vVT9HI9M</a><br />\n佢本身係抒情女高 但係音色偏暗比較厚 共鳴腔體打得算開 <br />\n早期胸腔多但係聽上去比較重 最近明顯向頭腔發展 而且偶爾會用到面罩共鳴<br />\n可以用調整唔同頭腔、胸腔嘅比例去營造唔同感覺<br />\n唱甜歌(e.g.一秒、哪裡只得我共你、次元壁等)頭聲比例多啲 聽上去仙氣啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9MkfzUOtHqE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9MkfzUOtHqE&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=14c5da15\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9MkfzUOtHqE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q8VMHax65JI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq8VMHax65JI&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=0be72701\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q8VMHax65JI</a><br />\n唱激勵啲嘅歌(e.g.鳥籠、失戀的人站起來)就用多啲胸聲 聽上去有力啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yNZTWAAWLLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyNZTWAAWLLw&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=58d1aac1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yNZTWAAWLLw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DtUq9HpOMlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDtUq9HpOMlw&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=1f10fc14\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DtUq9HpOMlw</a>"},{"pid":"8c53f68efe8ee332c67d610f46d324268bb91cc3","tid":2400220,"uid":376741,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"超鍾意佢首《奇怪》同《忍》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc960f0edc89c01ddb3ae861329ea4cf195f378a","tid":2400220,"uid":367215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:24:02.000Z","msg":"佢發聲算通暢 但係早期技術唔好 高音壓縮做得唔好<br />\n姐係發聲點大 對比其他歌手發聲點細 佢的確比較嗌 對聲帶負荷大<br />\n低音偶爾壓低喉位 唔科學 但係佢聲帶唔耐磨<br />\n對比有啲歌手就算唔科學咁唱都可以唱好耐 e.g. Christina Aguilera同早期GEM<br />\n再加上情緒同身體問題 佢經歷過幾次聲帶勞損 所以音色越來越沉<br />\n而且仲keep住用低喉位唱高音 對機能要求高<br />\n中間16~17年唱高音會好吃力<br />\n不過佢後期高音識壓縮(參考佢2019演唱會)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WM4OgTKbSLs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWM4OgTKbSLs&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=5667926b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WM4OgTKbSLs</a>  14秒D5<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xiXAMT0F4Kk  \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxiXAMT0F4Kk%20%20&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=8e564829\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xiXAMT0F4Kk  </a> 10幾個E5+D#5<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9ruWreK9uIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9ruWreK9uIo&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=4fcaea95\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9ruWreK9uIo</a><br />\n唔會再用咁多胸聲唱歌 不過已經冇當初咁敢唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wNq9HDX0PiE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwNq9HDX0PiE&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=5896a76d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wNq9HDX0PiE</a>  主歌好多D3  後面D5轉E5加好多B4咬字 (不過呢場狀態0分)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XNARxhNHHfE \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXNARxhNHHfE%20&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=6600a4c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XNARxhNHHfE </a> 主歌低音"},{"pid":"cf31ce4594f3d021e9062dc218671de4ffbabecb","tid":2400220,"uid":367215,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:25:25.000Z","msg":"不過mag佢聲帶有問題<br />\n有時候會控制唔住然後唱到劈左<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kn53r9lB408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fkn53r9lB408&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=5d52dffa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kn53r9lB408</a><br />\n最後head voice F5~F#5劈到老母都唔認得<br />\n而且全晚佢狀態好好都會破音 基本功都唔夠好 所以音準有時候會偏低<br />\n不過最大問題都係唔夠氣<br />\n有時候support唔到佢唱落去就會好吃力然後出現啲失誤同埋啲鼻音老牛聲出曬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以佢雖然vocal好但係live時好時壞"},{"pid":"4fc19706ab85e66555a7c2f2751c2205c524b150","tid":2400220,"uid":367215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:26:36.000Z","msg":"以前依家同未來都係錄音室時代<br />\n喺人聲上面更著重語感、音色、細節打磨、處理等等統稱叫「演唱意識」嘅野<br />\n搵到屬於自己嘅聲音人格 強調個人嘅處理方式加入唔同細節去打磨一首歌<br />\n練歌比練聲重要<br />\n所以其實mag呢啲係香港真係買少見少的<br />\n而且其實佢語感處理呢啲都可圈可點的<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eAiY4jKPiUI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeAiY4jKPiUI&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=89702666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eAiY4jKPiUI</a> 呢首歌歌詞on99 但係唱得好聽<br />\n仲有上面的一秒、哪裡只得我共你"},{"pid":"179df6eb2f23f78964953311941557ad3a334c43","tid":2400220,"uid":367215,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:28:06.000Z","msg":"就係因為mag呢啲係香港真係買少見少的<br />\n80、90後係vocal好好的只有容祖兒、GIN LEE、GEM同MAG<br />\n然後vocal幾好的得翻欣宜、JW、蔚雨芯、許靖韻等等<br />\n不過mag真係無人問津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真deserves more 起碼比人知道其實佢唱得都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度推薦幾首mag嘅歌比大家<br />\n鳥籠、洗澡、非同兒戲、我愛你、樹藤、一千零一次人生、光源、我們都是這樣長大的、奇怪、一秒"},{"pid":"e5ab8201a1ec46306788d0c3593188a558639be8","tid":2400220,"uid":367215,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:32:22.000Z","msg":"至於嗌歌呢方面佢已經冇嗌好耐 mag啲多歌多高音係真的<br />\n但係通常都係唱一兩句 咁一兩句高音我諗應該唔叫嗌歌嘅<br />\n成段都高音咁真係得翻a.i.n.y同手下敗將呢啲<br />\n不過已經好多年冇唱過呢啲歌了<br />\n所以希望大家唔好覺得林欣彤日日鳩叫<br />\n人都會變同進步的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03b06df1b89e25984e39e97bc06558b06f795b3","tid":2400220,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:35:06.000Z","msg":"其實點聽得咁清楚呢d音域幾多度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0a849842235ef800d80fe09012ee2d55492982","tid":2400220,"uid":340574,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:45:42.000Z","msg":"好老實講 聲線點音域點都好 係認得佢把聲<br />\n但佢把聲唱出嚟既野引唔起人有共嗚 牽動唔到人<br />\n仲會有少少厭佢個發音位置<br />\n係咁上下<br />\n<br />\n有時呢啲都好講觀眾口味同聽眾緣"},{"pid":"35a95fe6adca3ed55a19ee630f649bbb24d913fd","tid":2400220,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"179df6eb2f23f78964953311941557ad3a334c43","tid":2400220,"uid":367215,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T18:28:06.000Z","msg":"就係因為mag呢啲係香港真係買少見少的<br />\n80、90後係vocal好好的只有容祖兒、GIN LEE、GEM同MAG<br />\n然後vocal幾好的得翻欣宜、JW、蔚雨芯、許靖韻等等<br />\n不過mag真係無人問津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真deserves more 起碼比人知道其實佢唱得都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度推薦幾首mag嘅歌比大家<br />\n鳥籠、洗澡、非同兒戲、我愛你、樹藤、一千零一次人生、光源、我們都是這樣長大的、奇怪、一秒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"因為你推薦我會Spotify 聽幾日試下"},{"pid":"86797a4416df3355c095e57f3de5e136d542593a","tid":2400220,"uid":3093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T19:18:51.000Z","msg":"覺得佢初期音色普遍都係偏暗，成日唱到好混濁、鬼食泥咁<br />\n而家音色變化多咗，但控制力好似麻麻，尤其係啲字一唱得快就會聽得出<br />\n希望佢vocal dynamics 可以再明顯同多變化啲<br />\n想講佢唱到E5咁上下時會有種歇斯底里嘅感覺，係幾有魅力"},